{"tid":1001430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔好死】【殮房逼爆】新年前夕停屍格不敷應用 醫院指可能「一格放兩屍」惹爭議","createTime":"2019-01-30T06:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T06:55:19.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0937b68a989572f0df302c6f915c87bdefed5f21","tid":1001430,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190130/large/1548828117_db7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190130%2Flarge%2F1548828117_db7e.jpg&h=00d6ab6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港土地不足一屋難求，就連殮房屍體存放格也要「一格放兩屍」？！近日有市民到新界區的公立醫院求醫時，見到院內張貼了罕見的通告，通告指「因為殮房使用率持續高企」，若遺體數量超出可處理數量，院方可能會在殮房同一個存放格內放置兩具屍體，或是把部份遺體轉送其他醫院殮房存放。事主把相片上載到社交媒體時，慨嘆「真係由在生到死後都要排隊同迫」，惹來熱議，有網民質疑院方做法對死者不太尊重，擔心會不小心出現「屍叠屍」的情況，但亦有市民撐醫院，認為若停屍格不足，實在也沒有辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190130/large/1548830159_01fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190130%2Flarge%2F1548830159_01fa.jpg&h=6c0eb4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫院殮房瀕爆滿，有醫院貼出通告指可能要把兩具遺體放於同一冷藏存放格之內，引起爭議。（張培生攝）<br />\n<br />\n該張貼於新界區公立醫院的通知指「殮房使用率持續高企。請注意，如殮房存放的遺體超出可處理數量，院方會將死者遺體與另一同性別死者遺體暫放同一存放格內，或轉送到其他公立醫院殮房存放，作為臨時紓緩措施」。通告又呼籲死者家屬出一分力：「為避免殮房出現擠迫情況，請盡早領取死者遺體。不便之處，敬請體諒。」<br />\n貼相的羅先生留言慨嘆：「未死的在醫院等到想死&hellip;真的死了亦沒辦法被尊重&hellip;真係由在生到死後都要排隊同迫...未死的人，你慢慢等下啦，冇床位呀，你都未死得；死了的人，你快x啲走啦，冇雪櫃呀！」<br />\n有關相片引來不少人留言，有人指好恐怖，指「死了也沒尊嚴」，擔心會不慎出現屍叠屍情況。有人慨嘆若一格放兩屍，「死者(恐怕)生前都未試過另一個陌生人咁親近」，並嘆稱「死都冇位」，希望政府正視有關問題。<br />\n有在殮房任職人士則向《蘋果》表示，每逢冬季及新年前，都是殮房的「旺季」，殮房的使用率較高，致醫院存放屍體的冷藏「存放格」有機會爆滿，其中部份原因是有些人遲遲未領走家屬遺體，致遺體可能「滯留」殮房數個月甚至半年，加劇了殮房存放格不足的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190130/59202486?fbclid=IwAR2B1gPY7bK5qQ1w0wMV9TKasT0BMsYFZqvHUCuDmu0UTa9OvGUEXr65P20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190130%2F59202486%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2B1gPY7bK5qQ1w0wMV9TKasT0BMsYFZqvHUCuDmu0UTa9OvGUEXr65P20&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=d24df24f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190130%2F59202486%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2B1gPY7bK5qQ1w0wMV9TKasT0BMsYFZqvHUCuDmu0UTa9OvGUEXr65P20&h=c455c214\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190130/59202486?fbclid=IwAR2B1gPY7bK5qQ1w0wMV9TKasT0BMsYFZqvHUCuDmu0UTa9OvGUEXr65P20</a>"},{"pid":"8c5b9a4d1d5e4bf388484220e9712965e2973643","tid":1001430,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7730e7eb57092af99afdb8d1f620b6662ccdc7","tid":1001430,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e483555edfec91a4be153cb1753d524c44b53ae1","tid":1001430,"uid":62822,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a82d86f8bbd309eaca7706093cf8cc2ac30f2cc","tid":1001430,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:53:12.000Z","msg":"唸起 納粹集中營 焚屍爐"},{"pid":"0fc97a027202e865cf41156d089e543ca5c0644b","tid":1001430,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"送去777屋企存放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d960d661c98e380384b440d84491c50b7f82122c","tid":1001430,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"死都冇位擺 痴撚線"},{"pid":"eb2a8215542e230c5986c4ee2ac57ca7230ca218","tid":1001430,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"同正苦傾停屍迷你倉有得諗"},{"pid":"a22954d8f32a6e567404329003c81c5461c300a6","tid":1001430,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"香港真係痴撚左線 完全唔係人住"}]}